<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Property Management Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .info-section {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .value {
            color: #6b7280;
            width: 60%;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üè¢ Property Management Application</h1>
        <p>New application received on <%= date %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Application Details</h2>
        
        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>üë§ Personal Information</h3>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Full Name:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= fullName %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Email:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= email %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Phone Number:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= phoneNumber %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>üè† Property Information</h3>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Property Type:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= propertyType %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Number of Properties:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= numberOfProperties %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>üìç Property Address</h3>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Street Address:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= address.street %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Area:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= address.area %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Local Government:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= address.localGovernment %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">State:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= address.state %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>üí∞ Management Fee Agreement</h3>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">AGREED</span></p>
            <p>The applicant has agreed to the 5% management fee on all rental income generated from their properties under Aplet360's management.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>üìã Next Steps</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Property Assessment:</strong> Schedule a property inspection and valuation</li>
                <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Prepare management agreement and legal documents</li>
                <li><strong>Market Analysis:</strong> Conduct rental market analysis for optimal pricing</li>
                <li><strong>Onboarding:</strong> Set up property profile and marketing materials</li>
                <li><strong>Tenant Acquisition:</strong> Begin marketing and tenant screening process</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>‚è∞ Response Timeline</h3>
            <p>Please contact the applicant within <strong>24-48 hours</strong> to schedule the initial consultation and property assessment.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This application was submitted through the Aplet360 Property Management portal.</p>
        <p>For questions, contact: property-management@aplet360.com</p>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Aplet360. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
